                          <SHORT-NAME>COMM_EXCLUSIVE_AREA_2</SHORT-NAME>
                          <DESC>
                            <L-2 L="FOR-ALL">This exclusive area is only used in case of multi-partition. It must be configured as a spinlock to allow access to some variables simultaneously from multiple cores.</L-2>
                          </DESC>
